data.description: Welcome to this inviting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch located in the desirable area of Southfield. This home is move-in ready, waiting for you to make it your own. As you enter, you're greeted by wonderful hardwood floors in the main living area, adding warmth and charm to the space. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring great countertops and cabinet space, making cooking a breeze. Each bedroom offers ample space and good closet space, providing comfortable accommodations for everyone in the family. This home is ready for you to customize and transform into your dream home. Step outside and enjoy the summer nights on your patio, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Don't miss your opportunity to own this fantastic home—schedule your showing today
